<view class="page">
  <view class="card">
    <text class="card-title">分享与收藏</text>
    <text>右上角菜单中可进行“转发/朋友圈/收藏”。</text>
    <text class="meta">离场保存时间：{{ savedAt || '无' }}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <text class="card-title">运行时分享数据（wevu 钩子）</text>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">分享标题</text>
      <input class="field-input" value="{{ shareTitle }}" placeholder="输入分享标题" bindinput="onShareTitleInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">分享路径</text>
      <input class="field-input" value="{{ sharePath }}" placeholder="/pages/share/index" bindinput="onSharePathInput" />
    </view>
    <text class="meta">onShareAppMessage / onShareTimeline / onAddToFavorites 均读取这里的响应式值</text>
  </view>
</view>
